# Visualization Components

Components in this directory render ContentBlock variants from JSON data.

## Conventions

- Each component handles one ContentBlock type
- Props match the ContentBlock's data fields directly
- No internal state or data fetching — pure presentational
- Optional `caption` prop rendered as `Typography variant="caption"`
- Heavy chart libraries (Recharts): use `React.lazy()` and `<Suspense fallback={null}>`
- Colors: use theme-consistent values or accept via props, no hardcoded hex outside theme.ts

## Existing Components

| Component | ContentBlock type | Library |
|-----------|-------------------|---------|
| StatGrid | stat_grid | MUI only |
| ComparisonView | comparison | MUI only |
| RangeBarChart | range_bar | MUI only |
| SimpleBarChart | bar_chart | Recharts (lazy) |
| TimelineView | timeline | MUI only |
| ProgressStack | progress_stack | MUI only |
